### Variables ###
# Set mod key (Mod1=<Alt>, Mod4=<Super>)
set $alt	Mod1
set $mod 	Mod4
set $term	kitty

### Fonts ###
font pango:Symbols Nerd Font Mono, Iosevka Nerd Font Propo Heavy 12

